2 - \frac{4}{3} + \frac{8}{9} - \cdots + \frac{(-1)^{20}2^{21}}{3^{20}}
\sum\limits_{n=0}^{20} \frac{(-1)^{n}2^{n+1}}{3^{n}},
r \ne 1
r
S
rS
S = a + ar + \cdots + ar^{n - 1}
rS = ar + ar^2 + \cdots + ar^n.
rS - S = ar^n - a
S(r - 1) = ar^n - a.
S = a\frac{r^n - 1}{r - 1}.
\sum_{n=1}^{20}\frac{(-1)^n2^{n+1}}{3^n}=2\sum_{n=1}^{20}\left(-\frac{2}{3}\right)^n=2\left(-\frac{2}{3}\right)\frac{\left(-\frac{2}{3}\right)^{20}-1}{\left(-\frac{2}{3}-1\right)}=
=\left(-\frac{4}{3}\right)\left(-\frac{3}{5}\right)\frac{2^{20}-3^{20}}{3^{20}}=\frac{4}{5}\frac{2^{20}-3^{20}}{3^{20}}
